## Third-party components

This license covers sipher's own code. Vendored and third-party components
retain their own licenses (see `adapters/README.md` §라이선스 원칙):

- `adapters/threads/` — vendored from vdite/threads-scraper (MIT, see
  `adapters/threads/LICENSE`).
- `adapters/web/engine/` — vendored from fivetaku/insane-search (MIT, see
  `adapters/web/engine/LICENSE`).
- `gallery-dl` (tiktok adapter) — GPL-2.0, invoked as a separate subprocess
  only (not linked/vendored); no license propagation to sipher.
- `instaloader` (MIT), `yt-dlp` (Unlicense), `markitdown` (MIT), `playwright`,
  `curl_cffi`, `parsel`, `pyyaml`, `requests` — used as pip dependencies under
  their respective licenses.
